      "role": "user",
      "content": "Sometimes I look in the mirror and I dont even see myself anymore. I feel like the person I actually was—the one with the dreams and the spark—died a long time ago. Now I’m just... I'm just a walking corpse. Just going through the motions of a life that doesn't belong to me anymore.",
