      "content": "But there is no \"becoming\" something else. That's the problem. There's nothing left to build on. It's like trying to build a house on top of a grave. Everything I do feels hollow because the thing that made me *me* is just... gone. It's just empty space where a person used to be. It doesn't feel like a new beginning, it just feels like a burden to keep dragging this hollow shell around.",
